item.title: Hello, World!
item.author: vvelikodny@gmail.com (Vitaly Velikodnyi)
item.description: Hello! I’m Vitaly. Software Developer from Russia, Gopher. It’s my first post here just to say “hello” to all of you guys: human beings and robots! I will write here for a human being, but if you are a robot you are welcome too.
